title: Two Story Loft - Flexible Workspaces and Onsite Tesla Rental!
posting_body: ['Welcome to The Modern', 'Welcome to The Modern where first impressions are everything.', 'From the gracious greeting, you will receive upon arrival to the natural materials and finishes that act as an extension of the surrounding beauty, every detail has been carefully curated.', 'Beginning on the 13th floor, every one of our residences has a breathtaking panoramic view of Elliott Bay or the Seattle skyline with striking floor-to-ceiling windows.', 'The Conservatory is the heart of the building.', 'An exclusive club hall for a vertical neighborhood made up of six unique spaces that enliven two floors of the building: The Foyer, The Bar, The Video Wall, The Club Room, The Loft, and multiple private dining / executive board rooms.', 'The immediate area is rich with dozens of cultural attractions, restaurants, and nightlife options within walking distance, placing The Modern at the front steps of recreation.', 'Amenities Include:', 'Package service and in-home delivery', 'Laundry and dry-cleaning services', 'After-hours snack menu', 'View dome butler service', 'Children’s Studio with day care available', 'Paddleboard and bike rentals', 'Restaurant reservations and recommendations', 'In-home personal bartender', '24-hour front desk coverage', 'Car washing and in-house luxury car share', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', '*Pricing and availability are subject to change daily.', 'Photos may not be of the exact advertised unit.', 'Please contact us today for the most up to date information!']
